text: Dad Fatihana railway station () is a disused railway station on the Karachi–Peshawar Railway Line located in Dad Fatihana village, Punjab, Pakistan. The station is located east of Chichawatni railway station and west of Harappa railway station. ==See also== * List of railway stations in Pakistan * Pakistan Railways ==References== ==External links== *Official Web Site of Pakistan Railways Category:Railway stations in Sahiwal District Category:Defunct railway stations in Pakistan
